des:
Are you a huge Toronto Raptors fan? Then you need the Raptors Rapture Flash Briefing Skill by FanSided to get the latest news, opinions and rumors on the Toronto Raptors. 

The Raptors Rapture is a news and opinion site for fans of the Toronto Raptors brought to you by the FanSided Network dedicated to providing top-notch news, views and original content. This site also serves as a community for like-minded fans to come together to catch up on the latest news and to discuss their passion.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
